---
title: Honey-Soy Beef Tacos with Speedy Pickled Onion & Crispy Shallots
description: You think you know tacos? Think again. Our Asian-style beef filling changes the whole flavour profile of these tacos with its sweet and salty honey-soy glaze. Top them with crisp veggies and a punchy pickled onion for maximum enjoyment of this game-changer in fusion cuisine.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/korean-beef-tacos-2a48e9d5.jpg
